{"tid":1076939,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯與C朗 系列 之 排陣","createTime":"2019-03-25T08:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T11:55:33.000Z","uid":176368,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"31bc8aa4d5b248a47d50cdcb2a2af4118cb0da4f","tid":1076939,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:26:36.000Z","msg":"上回：美斯與C朗 系列 之 簡介<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1076765/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1076765/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n二擇其一，作爲領隊你會想要邊個？<br />\n<br />\n美斯同C朗都係反擊高手，<br />\n主攻時雖然角色唔一樣，<br />\n但作用都非常關鍵，<br />\n視乎你嘅組軍方向。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>美斯</strong><br />\n要發揮 轉型後美斯 的最大效果，<br />\n就要放喺球隊中心，周圍有隊友，<br />\n左右出配合型翼鋒，負責拉邊插入，<br />\n前面有二傳高手（唔需要美斯背龍踢），<br />\n後面有兩個防中（無需要美斯回防）。<br />\n如果太依賴個人能力而非穩定結構，<br />\n佢狀態差、年紀大就會出事。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>C朗</strong><br />\n球隊中前場要有人出到波畀佢，<br />\n有速度型球員配合更好，<br />\n其他位置放咩人甚至陣式都對C朗冇乜影響，<br />\n觸發最大效果門檻較低。<br />\n當然球隊需要半主角或主角球員組織。"},{"pid":"0dc94aaa74850f6a0ea086f33f39f02b98d745e9","tid":1076939,"uid":134997,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:28:33.000Z","msg":"c朗要半主角/主角<br />\n咁點解大波奶無得出<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e10becaf955fa013a0ae9447953f78512851881","tid":1076939,"uid":53855,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:29:01.000Z","msg":"巴塞體系真係發揮美斯到最大威力"},{"pid":"58328111617ca7305b48c0c56e644a30ca27afa5","tid":1076939,"uid":179979,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:29:10.000Z","msg":"領隊要美c<br />\n老闆要c7"},{"pid":"5a5d859550f8fe817675cca53cb211cc18b812c1","tid":1076939,"uid":90515,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:29:29.000Z","msg":"又係陰啲陰啲反美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd3b5da60e331e70583b428327d5103f913c814","tid":1076939,"uid":176368,"like":1,"dislike":